HEADWORD: bootlicker
<hw>bootlicker</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>someone who humbles himself as a
sign of respect; who behaves as he had no self-respect.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> apple polisher, bootlick, fawner, groveller,
truckler, ass-kisser, toady.</syn>⟦br⟧
